description: Having trouble creating a crock pot recipe on Don't Starve? Don't fret! Don't Starve Crock Pot Recipe help you list all the recipe from dragon pie to monster tartare. Just say ask crockpot item and the helper will tell you the recipe.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, Ask Don't Starve CrockPot Helper, how do you make a dragon pie
Alexa, Ask Don't Starve CrockPot Helper, what do I need for dragon pie
Alexa, Ask Don't Starve CrockPot Helper, recipe for dragon pie
name: Don't Starve CrockPot Helper
shortDescription:
Don't Starve Crock Pot Recipe Guide.
The helper help you list all the ingredients you need for a recipe.
